Use the standard library
This is how to triples_sum_to_zero of l:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this l's length times:
      Remember that j is sum of i and 1
      Do this (diff of l's length and (sum of i and 1)) times:
         Remember that k is sum of j and 1
         Do this (diff of l's length and (sum of j and 1)) times:
            Remember that total is sum of item i in l and item j in l and item k in l
            When total is 0, then:
               Increase count
            End when
            Increase k
         End do
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
